1808
01:51:57,995 --> 01:51:58,795
Good morning.

1809
01:51:58,879 --> 01:52:00,922
JENKINS: There are a few rules to be observed.

1810
01:52:03,092 --> 01:52:05,176
Here's a complete list of the Conlon, Guiseppe case files,

1811
01:52:05,260 --> 01:52:07,053
