1812
01:52:07,137 --> 01:52:09,305
I'll go to the file drawer and bring it out.

1813
01:52:09,807 --> 01:52:11,557
You'll open it in front of me, take a page at a time,

1814
01:52:11,642 --> 01:52:13,309
read it, and then return it.

1815
01:52:13,394 --> 01:52:15,436
Is there a problem, Mr. Dixon?

1816
01:52:15,562 --> 01:52:17,105
Problem? Not at all, Mrs. Peirce.

1817
01:52:17,189 --> 01:52:20,650
Our chief archivist, Mr. Jenkins, is here to assist you.

1818
01:52:21,652 --> 01:52:23,945
If you want to make a photocopy, I and I alone will do it,

1819
01:52:24,029 --> 01:52:26,239
