1826
01:52:43,507 --> 01:52:45,591
Conlon, Guiseppe file.

1827
01:52:45,676 --> 01:52:46,968
MAN: Yes, sir.

1828
01:53:00,274 --> 01:53:01,607
Might as well leave my kit on the bus,

1829
01:53:01,692 --> 01:53:03,234
